  "subject": "Update Dockerfiles to Java 17",
  "commit_message": "Update Dockerfiles to Java 17\n\nMigrate all Dockerfiles from Java 11 to eclipse-temurin:17-jre-alpine\nfor consistency with the Java 17 build migration.\n\n- Dockerfile.so-base-image: eclipse-temurin:11-jre-alpine -> 17-jre-alpine\n- Dockerfile.adapters: onap/integration-java11:7.0.0 -> eclipse-temurin:17-jre-alpine\n  with explicit so user/permissions setup\n- so-simulator Dockerfile: openjdk:11-jre-slim -> eclipse-temurin:17-jre-alpine\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4316\nChange-Id: Ic9398a8a1cf1a899613064c5346b6537d656efe5\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
